tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumSimulations (
    simulation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    circuit_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    num_qubits INT NOT NULL,
    algorithm_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    execution_time INTERVAL NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE circuits (
  circuit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  circuit_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  qubits INT,
  gates INT
)

CREATE TABLE measurements (
  measurement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  circuit_id INT,
  measurement_result VARCHAR(255),
  FOREIGN KEY (circuit_id) REFERENCES circuits(circuit_id)
)

CREATE TABLE algorithms (
  algorithm_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  algorithm_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  quantum_computer VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE performances (
  performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  algorithm_id INT,
  circuit_id INT,
  execution_time DECIMAL,
  FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES algorithms(algorithm_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (circuit_id) REFERENCES circuits(circuit_id)
)

CREATE TABLE simulations (
    simulation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    simulation_name STRING,
    circuit_id UUID,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);
